Jute is a plant grown with the Farming skill at level 13 Farming. Jute is grown by planting 3 jute seeds in a hops patch using a seed dibber.

After 10 minutes or less, the planted seed will become Jute. The hops patch must be raked clean of weeds. Once planted, the nearby farmer may be paid to watch over the hops at the cost of 6 barley malt

Jute plants take 50 minutes to mature. An Amulet of nature may be bound to the patch to provide progress on its growth. Once mature, the hops produces up to 35 Jute at a time without compost and 65 with ultracompost.

Planting the jute seeds gives 13 farming experience. No xp is given for checking on the hops. If the farmer does not watch the hops patch, then disease on the patch may be removed using plant cure. However, if left alone, the diseased patch will die.

Each jute, when picked, gives 14.5 farming experience. The jute do not grow back after they are picked. The jute may be picked after the plant is completely grown.
